title: Minor changes
message:

title: Updates for multiple timestamps support
message:
Updates for multiple timestamps support

Changed DatabaseHelper UpdateWords method to update also the Timestamps
table

title: Timestamps accessor
message:
Timestamps accessor

Added accessor method in Statistics class for Timestamps

title: Multiple timestamps modifications
message:
Multiple timestamps modifications

Added Timestamps table in the database. Added comments in the
DatabaseHelper class wherever it needs changes to support multiple
timestamps. I kept the timestamp column in the Words table in order to
keep it backward compatible (and gain some time in order to not quering
for the last timestamp of a word).

title: Statistics module now supports multiple timestamps
message:
Statistics module now supports multiple timestamps

Replaced the timestamp data member with a list of timestamps. The last
timestamp is always the first element of the arraylist.
